<h4 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h4>
<p>Suppose we throw two  balls straight up. If the first has  an initial velocity of <span class="process-math">\(v_0\)</span> and the second has an initial velocity of <span class="process-math">\(2v_0\)</span> will the maximum height of the  second ball be twice the maximum height of the first. (Again, we ignore air resistance.)</p>
<span class="incontext"><a href="section-3.html#p-40" class="internal">in-context</a></span>
